Data from repository for the 2019 Novel Coronavirus Visual Dashboard operated by the Johns Hopkins University Center for Systems Science and Engineering (JHU CSSE). Also, countries and continents from dbouquin.

LATAM has just 1.22 percent of world wide cases.
